{
  "stem": "7177.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In other words, there's got to be order in this place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I think, after all these years, I still live by that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Everything has to be in its place so that you can find everything within two seconds.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that was-- Then she was an excellent seamstress.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She had worked in Frankfurt an Mein before she was married to my father and had done an awful lot of-- made dresses and costumes for people in the theater.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she was-- so she knew a lot about theater.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we were very musically-- well, there was no entertainment in this little town unless we did it ourselves.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So of the four of us, the three of us, except my younger brother Harry, we all play the piano.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And my older brother taught me the original notes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then later on, I went to piano lessons, where the nuns taught me to play the piano better than what I knew in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The original piano lesson was on a little play piano that had eight notes on it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So that's my first experience there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And it was just-- Then I wanted to let you know how we lived at home.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "In this small town where there was absolutely no entertainment, we had-- very hard to believe nowadays-- two newspapers, a morning newspapers and an evening newspaper.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And my father-- we would sit around a table at night, all of us, either making homework or my mother darning socks.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "That time, we didn't have nylon socks, so the socks had to be darned.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And my father then would read the newspaper aloud to all of us, got me interested in politics when I was about five, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
